<h2 id="provenance">Provenance</h2>

<h3 id="winery">Winery</h3>
<p>Penfolds Max‚Äôs Cabernet Sauvignon is a tribute to former Chief Winemaker Max Schubert (1948-1975), a legend in Penfolds history. Max‚Äôs constant pursuit of excellence paved the way for those who followed in his footsteps and also allowed the status and heritage of Penfolds to grow. Max‚Äôs Cabernet Sauvignon displays the Penfolds ‚Äòstamp‚Äô inspired by Max Schubert.</p>
